pageProduct.name: Redwin Collagen Glow Skin Firming Cream 220g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Enhance skin elasticity and firmness with 100% pure collagen to nourish and rejuvenate your skin for an all over glow.

Collagen levels in your skin deplete as we age, that's why Redwin Collagen Glow has been formulated to restore collagen levels for brighter, firmer and younger looking skin. It will work to:
- Add moisture to the skin for softer, smoother skin
- Enhance skin elasticity for firmer skin
- Reduce the appearance of wrinkles for younger looking skin

Suitable For: Sensitive skin

Size: 220g

Warnings

Warning: Keep away from eyes

Ingredients

Ingredients: Water, Paraffinum Liquidum, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate, Dimethicone, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Myristyl Myristate, Stearic Acid, PEG-100 Stearate, Phenoxyethanol, Carbomer, Chlorphenesin, Beeswax, Myristyl Laurate, Sodium Hydroxide, Disodium EDTA, Tocopheryl Acetate, BHT, Proprolene Glycol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract, Maltodextrin, Sorbitol, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Citric Acid, Soluble Collagen, Sodium Citrate, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Sorbate, Ethylhexylglycerin.

Contains: N/A

Allergen Contains: Null

Allergen May Be Present: Null

Allergen Free From: n/a

Directions

Directions: Apply daily to face, neck, legs, all over body

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30°C
